high_descs: Turn left and walk to the room to reach the sink.
Pick up the bowl from the counter on the sink.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Cool the bowl in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold bowl in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink.
Grab the clear bowl from the left side of the sink.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bowl on the middle shelf then remove the bowl.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Place the bowl into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the bowl from the sink.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the bowl into the fridge.
Take it out and go near the microwave.
Put the bowl into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the bowl into the microwave.
